<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Mizu Research</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
      <section id="welcome-section" class="col-12" style="position: relative;">
        <%= image_tag('pic.png', alt: "Services Image", style: "position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; z-index: -1;") %>
        <div class="content-overlay">
          <h1 class="section-title">Welcome to Mizu Research</h1>
          <p class="section-description">Find the perfect solution for your research.</p>
          <%= link_to "Browse Tasks", "/tasks", class: "btn btn-outline-primary" %>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <section id="about-section" class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>
        <p class="section-description">We connect talented freelancers with clients seeking their skills.</p>
      </section>
      <section id="services-section" class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Services</h2>
        <ul class="service-list list-group">
          <li class="list-group-item">Academic</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Business</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Technology</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Government</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <section id="testimonial-section" class="col-12">
        <h2 class="section-title">Client Testimonials</h2>
        <div class="testimonial card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <blockquote>
              "I found the perfect freelancer for my project. The platform made it easy to connect and collaborate."
            </blockquote>
            <cite>- John Doe, Client</cite>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <section id="portfolio-section" class="col-12">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Portfolio</h2>
        <p class="section-description">Check out some of the amazing projects that our freelancers have delivered.</p>
        <div class="card-columns">
          <div class="card">
            <%= image_tag('pic.png', alt: "Project 1", class: "card-img-top") %>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Project 1</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <%= image_tag('pic.png', alt: "Project 2", class: "card-img-top") %>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Project 2</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <%= image_tag('pic.png', alt: "Project 3", class: "card-img-top") %>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Project 3</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- ... -->
        </div>
      </section>      
    </div>    
    <div class="row">
      <section id="contact-section" class="col-12">
        <h2 class="section-title">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="section-description">Have a question? Reach out to our team for assistance.</p>
        <%= link_to "Contact Us", "/contact", class: "btn btn-outline-secondary" %>
      </section>      
    </div>    
    <div class="row">
      <section id="blog-section" class="col-12">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Blog</h2>
        <p class="section-description">Read our latest articles on freelancing and hiring.</p>        
        <ul class="blog-list list-unstyled">
          <li class="media">
            <%= image_tag('pic.png', alt: "Blog 1", class: "mr-3") %>
            <div class="media-body">
              <h5 class="mt-0 mb-1">How to write a great project description</h5>
              <p>A project description is the first thing that a freelancer sees when browsing for tasks. Learn how to write a clear and concise description that attracts the best talent.</p>
              <%= link_to "Read More", "/blog/1", class: "btn btn-outline-primary" %>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="media">
            <%= image_tag('pic.png', alt: "Blog 2", class: "mr-3") %>
            <div class="media-body">
              <h5 class="mt-0 mb-1">How to manage your time as a freelancer</h5>
              <p>Time management is one of the most important skills for a freelancer. Learn how to plan your schedule, prioritize your tasks, and avoid distractions.</p>
              <%= link_to "Read More", "/blog/2", class: "btn btn-outline-primary" %>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="media">
            <%= image_tag('pic.png', alt: "Blog 3", class: "mr-3") %>
            <div class="media-body">
              <h5 class="mt-0 mb-1">How to communicate effectively with your clients</h5>
              <p>Communication is key for a successful freelance project. Learn how to establish trust, set expectations, and provide feedback with your clients.</p>
              <%= link_to "Read More", "/blog/3", class: "btn btn-outline-primary" %>
            </div>
          </li>
          <!-- ... -->
        </ul>        
      </section>      
    </div>    
  </div>

  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

